Maintainer: Joshua Lamos <jlamos@georgialibraries.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~), autotools-dev
Standards-Version: 3.8.4
Homepage: http://libdbi-drivers.sourceforge.net/

Package: libdbi-drivers
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libpq5
Description: implements a database-independent abstraction layer in C, similar to the DBI/DBD layer in Perl
 The libdbi-drivers project provides the database-specific drivers 
 for the libdbi framework. The current version of libdbi-drivers 
 will work with any 0.8.x release of the framework
